Persona 5 is probably one of the greatest JRPG’s in recent years. Developer Atlus was able to create a better and more beautiful game then it’s fantastic predecessor. The serie evolved with some great adjustments and few additions but stayed true to the series’ roots and gave the JRPG fans exactly what they want: a very special game to put lots of hours in. The story is unique and enjoyable, the battle system is fun and addictive and the variety of activities to engage in made this game worth the wait. Will this game be the Game Of The Year?
